Package org.eclipse.mosaic.fed.application.ambassador.simulation.perception.index.objects

Interface SpatialObjectBoundingBox

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PointBoundingBox, VehicleBoundingBox
    public interface SpatialObjectBoundingBox
extends Serializable
    This interface shall be implemented by all classes representing the bounding box of a SpatialObject. All points are returned in the global coordinate system as Vector3d.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method Description
      List<Vector3d> getAllCorners()
      Returns all corners spanning the 2D bounding box of a SpatialObject as global coordinates.
      List<Edge<Vector3d>> getAllEdges()
      Returns all sides spanning the 2D bounding box of a SpatialObject as edges in the global coordinate system.
